### Collection Templates

#### Blog Post Collection

```typescript
{
  name: 'post',
  label: 'Blog Posts',
  path: 'content/posts',
  format: 'mdx',
  fields: [
    {
      type: 'string',
      name: 'title',
      label: 'Title',
      isTitle: true,  // Shows in content list
      required: true
    },
    {
      type: 'string',
      name: 'excerpt',
      label: 'Excerpt',
      ui: {
        component: 'textarea'  // Multi-line input
      }
    },
    {
      type: 'image',
      name: 'coverImage',
      label: 'Cover Image'
    },
    {
      type: 'datetime',
      name: 'date',
      label: 'Published Date',
      required: true
    },
    {
      type: 'reference',
      name: 'author',
      label: 'Author',
      collections: ['author']  // References author collection
    },
    {
      type: 'boolean',
      name: 'draft',
      label: 'Draft',
      description: 'If checked, post will not be published',
      required: true
    },
    {
      type: 'rich-text',
      name: 'body',
      label: 'Body',
      isBody: true  // Main content area
    }
  ],
  ui: {
    router: ({ document }) => `/blog/${document._sys.filename}`
  }
}
```

**Template**: See `templates/collections/blog-post.ts`

